<lb n="0423c13"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0423c14"/>
<lb n="0423c15"/><head type="no">No. 1305</head>
<lb n="0423c16"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><note n="0423061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】享保年間刊豐山大學藏本，【甲】久安五年寫東寺三密藏本，【乙】天永四年寫高野山寶壽院藏本</note><jhead>北斗七星念誦儀軌</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0423c17"/>
<lb n="0423c18"/><byline type="Translator">南天竺國三藏金剛智譯</byline>
<lb n="0423c19"/><div1 type="jing"><p>爾時如來為末<note n="0423062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">世＝在【甲】＊</note><app n="0423062"><lem>世</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">在</rdg></app>薄福一切眾生故。說真言
<lb n="0423c20"/>教法。時一切日月星宿。皆悉雲集前後圍繞。
<lb n="0423c21"/>異口同音<note n="0423063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔白言〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0423063"><lem>白言</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。唯願如來<note n="0423064" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔而為〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0423064"><lem>而為</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>我等說<note n="0423065" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔於〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0423065"><lem>於</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0423c22"/>神&CB00057;。于時<anchor id="fxT21p0423c01"/>世尊說八星&CB00057;曰。</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1305.0424a" n="0424a"/>
<lb n="0424a01"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd"><note n="0424001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">甲乙二本梵字闕</note>&SD-DA42;</t><t lang="chi">唵</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A67A;</t><t lang="chi">颯</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CEE4;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0424002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">跢＋（曩）【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424002"><lem>跢</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">跢曩</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A4B8;</t><t lang="chi">而</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5A9;</t><t lang="chi">曩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F1;</t><t lang="chi">野</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5D9;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0424003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">伴＝半【甲】</note><app n="0424003"><lem>伴</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">半</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B5ED;</t><t lang="chi">惹</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A658;</t><t lang="chi">密</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A4B6;</t><t lang="chi">惹</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F1;</t><t lang="chi">野</t></tt>
<lb n="0424a02"/>
<lb n="0424a03"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A4C0;</t><t lang="chi">染</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E042;</t><t lang="chi">普</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A563;</t><t lang="chi">他</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5E5;</t><t lang="chi">摩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B064;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>娑&CB00085;</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5E7;</t><t lang="chi">弭</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5A9;</t><t lang="chi">曩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5FD;</t><t lang="chi">囉</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6BE;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>乞山</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0424a04"/>
<lb n="0424a05"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5D9;</t><t lang="chi">婆</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A656;</t><t lang="chi">&CB00085;</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A55B;</t><t lang="chi">都</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA49;</t><t lang="chi">莎</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;</t><t lang="chi">呵</t></tt></p>
<lb n="0424a06"/>
<lb n="0424a07"/><p>其印<note n="0424004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">明＝相【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424004"><lem>明</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">相</rdg></app>出金剛頂經<note n="0424005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">七＝八【甲】</note><app n="0424005"><lem>七</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">八</rdg></app>星<note n="0424006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">品＋（勿妄宣傳為極祕密）【甲】，（口云曼殊八葉）【乙】</note><app n="0424006"><lem>品</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">品勿妄宣傳為極祕密</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">品口云曼殊八葉</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0424a08"/><p>佛告貪狼破軍<note n="0424007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">等言＝星等【甲】</note><app n="0424007"><lem>等言</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">星等</rdg></app>。若有善男子善女人。受
<lb n="0424a09"/>持<note n="0424008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＝此【甲】</note><app n="0424008"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">此</rdg></app>神<note n="0424009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00057;＋（者）【甲】</note><app n="0424009"><lem>&CB00057;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00057;者</rdg></app>擁護否。于時八<note n="0424010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">女＝星【甲】</note><app n="0424010"><lem>女</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">星</rdg></app>白世尊言。若
<lb n="0424a10"/>有人每日誦此神<note n="0424011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00057;＋（汝等）&M062403;【原】，（三七遍）【甲】</note><app n="0424011"><lem>&CB00057;</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&CB00057;汝等</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00057;三七遍</rdg></app>。決定罪<note n="0424012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">業＋（障）【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424012"><lem>業</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">業障</rdg></app>皆悉除滅。
<lb n="0424a11"/>成就一切願求。<note n="0424013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">設＝若【甲】</note><app n="0424013"><lem>設</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">若</rdg></app>復有人。若能每日誦此神
<lb n="0424a12"/>&CB00057;一<note n="0424014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔百八〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424014"><lem>百八</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0424015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">遍＝切【乙】</note><app n="0424015"><lem>遍</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">切</rdg></app>。即得自身及一切眷屬擁護。
<lb n="0424a13"/>若能誦五百遍。大威神<note n="0424016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">力＋（手）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0424016"><lem>力</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">力手</rdg></app>。五百由旬內。普
<lb n="0424a14"/>皆圍繞。一切魔王及<note n="0424017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諸＝法【甲】</note><app n="0424017"><lem>諸</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">法</rdg></app>魔<note n="0424018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔眾〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424018"><lem>眾</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。一切障者無
<lb n="0424a15"/>量惡<note n="0424019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鬼＋（神）【甲】</note><app n="0424019"><lem>鬼</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">鬼神</rdg></app>。不敢親近。常當擁護。北斗八女一
<lb n="0424a16"/>切日月星宿諸天龍藥叉。能作障難者一時
<lb n="0424a17"/>斷壞。<note n="0424020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">若＋（有）【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424020"><lem>若</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">若有</rdg></app>人欲供養者。先發拔濟心。於清淨
<lb n="0424a18"/><note n="0424021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔寂〕－【甲】，〔寂靜〕－【乙】</note><note n="0424021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔寂靜〕－【乙】，〔寂〕－【甲】</note><app n="0424021"><lem>寂靜</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">靜</rdg></app>之處。以香華飲食供養。持念神&CB00057;結印
<lb n="0424a19"/>契。如是供<note n="0424022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔養〕－【乙】</note><app n="0424022"><lem>養</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>時。<note n="0424023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（北斗）＋八【甲】</note><app n="0424023"><lem>八</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">北斗八</rdg></app>女及一切眷屬。現身隨
<lb n="0424a20"/>意奉仕。成就無量願求。<note n="0424024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惹位＝羅惹即王位&M062403;【原】，若求惹位【甲】，若惹位【乙】</note><note n="0424024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惹位＝羅惹即王位&M062403;【原】，＝若求惹位【甲】，＝若惹位【乙】</note><app n="0424024"><lem>惹位</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">羅惹即王位</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">若求惹位</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">若惹位</rdg></app>即得。何況世
<lb n="0424a21"/>間少<note n="0424025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">少＝小【乙】</note><app n="0424025"><lem>少</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">小</rdg></app>官位榮耀。若求壽<note n="0424026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">命＋（者）【甲】</note><app n="0424026"><lem>命</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">命者</rdg></app>削定業籍。還
<lb n="0424a22"/>付生籍。若諸國王王子大臣後宮等。於自<note n="0424027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">宮＝官【甲】</note><app n="0424027"><lem>宮</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">官</rdg></app>
<lb n="0424a23"/>中作曼荼<note n="0424028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羅＝利【甲】</note><app n="0424028"><lem>羅</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">利</rdg></app>。如法護摩禮拜供養。北斗八女
<lb n="0424a24"/>皆大歡喜。故久居勝位痡`受安樂。百官上
<lb n="0424a25"/>下和穆不行非法。人民熾盛稼穡豐饒。國土
<lb n="0424a26"/>安寧無有災難不現異怪。疫病死亡不起。境
<lb n="0424a27"/>內怨敵群賊自然退散。<note n="0424029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔故〕－【甲】</note><app n="0424029"><lem>故</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>以是法甚為祕密。
<lb n="0424a28"/>不信者及無智人中勿妄宣傳。無智人不分
<lb n="0424a29"/>明心故。不得法意生疑謗。雖無智<note n="0424030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔人〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424030"><lem>人</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>金剛生
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1305.0424b" n="0424b"/>
<lb n="0424b01"/>金剛子等。常誦持佛<note n="0424031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔眼〕－【甲】</note><app n="0424031"><lem>眼</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>母明者當宣傳。金
<lb n="0424b02"/>剛子雖無智不生疑謗故成就法。行者雖樂
<lb n="0424b03"/>世間樂。深迴向無上正等菩<note n="0424032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">提＋（北斗七星念誦法略半）【甲】</note><app n="0424032"><lem>提</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">提北斗七星念誦法略半</rdg></app><note n="0424033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此下甲本奧書云一校了久安五年七月一日書了賢覺，乙本奧書云以高野後僧正御持本展轉書了天永四年二月一日於性德院書之僧念範之本（朱）同日入寺御房奉受了</note>。</p></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>
